#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.132"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.132:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.132:0.2"
msgid "13. Avijjāvagga "
msgstr "13. Ignorance "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn22.132:0.3"
msgid "132. Dutiyasamudayasutta "
msgstr "132. Origin (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn22.132:1.1"
msgid "Bārāṇasiyaṃ viharanti isipatane migadāye … pe … "
msgstr "At Benares. "

msgctxt "sn22.132:1.2"
msgid "ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā mahākoṭṭhiko āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Mahākoṭṭhita said to Sāriputta: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.132:1.3"
msgid "“‘vijjā, vijjā’ti, āvuso sāriputta, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Reverend Sāriputta, they speak of this thing called ‘knowledge’. "

msgctxt "sn22.132:1.4"
msgid "Katamā nu kho, āvuso, vijjā; "
msgstr "What is knowledge? "

msgctxt "sn22.132:1.5"
msgid "kittāvatā ca vijjāgato hotī”ti? "
msgstr "And how is a knowledgeable person defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn22.132:2.1"
msgid "“Idhāvuso, sutavā ariyasāvako rūpassa samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. "
msgstr "“Reverend, an educated noble disciple truly understands the origin, the ending, the gratification, the drawback, and the escape when it comes to form, "

msgctxt "sn22.132:2.2"
msgid "Vedanāya … pe … "
msgstr "feeling, "

msgctxt "sn22.132:2.3"
msgid "saññāya … "
msgstr "perception, "

msgctxt "sn22.132:2.4"
msgid "saṅkhārānaṃ … "
msgstr "choices, "

msgctxt "sn22.132:2.5"
msgid "viññāṇassa samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. "
msgstr "and consciousness. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.132:2.6"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccatāvuso, vijjā; "
msgstr "This is called knowledge. "

msgctxt "sn22.132:2.7"
msgid "ettāvatā ca vijjāgato hotī”ti. "
msgstr "And this is how a knowledgeable person is defined.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.132:2.8"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
